videos.headline: Anderson finds Tyler for 31-yard Coastal Carolina TD
videos.description: Coastal Carolina QB Kilton Anderson connects with Ky'Jon Tyler for 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns' Mitchell erupts for 30-yard TD

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns' Calais bursts for 61-yard TD run
